◆ testCheckPrechargeIterateStub()

void testCheckPrechargeIterateStub ( void  )

Iterate over a callback that supplies various scenarios and check if they work as expected.

This function uses the callback MockDATA_ReadBlock_Callback() in order to inject current tables and voltage tables into the returned database tables. The array prechargeExpectedResults contains prepared return values against which the output of TEST_BMS_CheckPrecharge() is compared.
